In respect of the following documents, the fees to be collected by the Secretary of State for filing, when required by this chapter, shall be:
Articles of incorporation, eight dollars ($8);
Articles of amendment, eight dollars ($8);
Restated articles of incorporation, eight dollars ($8);
Articles of merger or consolidation, eight dollars ($8);
Articles of dissolution, five dollars ($5); and
Any other statement or report of a foreign or domestic corporation, eight dollars ($8).
